pelicop_pelishop-php.summary: Recent activities on pelicop_pelishop-php have been focused on implementing multiple functionalities, including enhancements to the shopping cart view and functionality in ClienteController, updates to carrito link, and product listing and creation functionality for Empresa. Refactoring efforts have also been noted, such as removing DOCS links, simplifying product filtering, and updating product display logic.

html_to_pdf_python.summary: The html_to_pdf_python repository has seen recent contributions focused on implementing a diploma generation feature, including input fields for diploma generation and the integration of PDF creation functionality. Miscellaneous updates, including .gitignore adjustments and a wxPython Hello World application with a GUI and menu, have also been made to the repository.

profile_summary:
As a skilled Full Stack Web Developer with 20+ public repositories, I leverage my expertise in Python, TypeScript, and JavaScript to drive innovative projects forward. 

A 19-year-old native of Venezuela, I bring a unique perspective to the tech industry and am passionate about staying atop emerging trends and technologies. I currently pursue a degree in Systems Engineering and continuously update my portfolio with new projects.
